title: Popeye (1980) - Robin Williams
description:
Released: 1980
From Paramount Pictures and Walt Disney Productions.

This movie version of the cartoon classic of Popeye starts at the beginning of the whole Popeye series. Which is also based off the comic book of Popeye. Popeye heads towards an island where he is introduced to the community of Sweethaven. That is where he meets up with Olive Oyl, the Oyl family, Wimpy, Swee\&#039;pea, and his big time bully Bluto for the very first time.

Popeye - Robin Williams
Olive Oyl - Shelly Duvall 
Poopdeck Pappy - Ray Walston
Wimpy - Paul Dooley
Bluto - Paul L. Smith
Swee\&#039;pea - Wesley Ivan Hurt

The movies were filmed in \"Popeye\&#039;s village\" on the Island of Malta
